desc.en: This is a Fast and Frequent transit map for my city in Cities:Skylines 2. It's references is from Vancouver Translink. This is a city mixed with Chineses and Americans. Line 3 Prospect Rd, E 3rd Street and Lloyd Ave station is called Jiefang Street, Tianfu Street and Gongchan Avenue. Well, enjoy I guess...
